{"tid":2176721,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"裁判官批准林卓廷各人保釋候訊","createTime":"2020-08-27T09:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T10:37:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"424f7fcb9cf66ae9d8d3b71662be88d3f99618a6","tid":2176721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=ddc70892\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM%2F&h=3349d022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晨就去年7.21元朗事件，以暴動罪拘捕13人，包括遭白衣人施襲受傷、一直要求追查事件真相的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷，令原告變被告；另拘捕林的黨友許智峯等另外3人，指他們去年7月「光復屯門公園」後，強迫一男子刪除手機內相片，涉嫌意圖妨礙司法公正、有犯罪及不誠實意圖取用電腦等。其中10人今午迅速在西九龍裁判法院提堂，林卓廷牽涉兩案。就721暴動案，控方稱仍有起碼廿名在逃人士，並反對所有被告保釋。但裁判官最終批准各人保釋候訊。"},{"pid":"60e3a92688aa0b8699964c7739325b133f2c80cf","tid":2176721,"uid":277934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"424f7fcb9cf66ae9d8d3b71662be88d3f99618a6","tid":2176721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=ddc70892\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM%2F&h=3349d022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/6Z2A5PZIWFHARHK6WI5ZVS3LLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晨就去年7.21元朗事件，以暴動罪拘捕13人，包括遭白衣人施襲受傷、一直要求追查事件真相的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷，令原告變被告；另拘捕林的黨